{"tid":1091202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"縱火燒大廈大堂信件 深水埗20歲仔被捕","createTime":"2019-04-04T03:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T03:37:50.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98c7a9130c5b612fab4a46414c997c42b41a59c3","tid":1091202,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GU4ZPGT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGU4ZPGT.png&h=4747f8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n探員到涉事大廈調查。梁瑞帆攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPvqLfe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPvqLfe.png&h=6ca4313e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保安員在場協查。梁瑞帆攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9mNd8A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9mNd8A.png&h=ebe8adce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大堂地面有熏黑痕迹。梁瑞帆攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jo4vbVg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJo4vbVg.png&h=9de24e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗汝州街175-177號一幢單幢式住宅大廈，地下大堂設有一排信箱，昨晚11時許，大堂一堆信件着火，住客發現報警求助，消防接報到場，迅速將火救熄。警員在場翻看cctv，發現一名青年潛入大廈內，在不同信箱拔出10多封信件，就地點火燃燒，警經調查後在附近拘捕該名20歲姓劉青年，涉嫌縱火。案件中無人受傷，毋須疏散。據了解，涉事大廈並無通宵更保安員，而被捕青年並非該大廈住客。警正調查其縱火動機。"}]}